==================================

I Survived... - Season 4 - HD 720p

==================================


Episode 1 - "Jennifer / Neely Ann" - May 15, 2011

A Palm Springs, California nurse is kidnapped and sexually tortured by a serial killer; and a mother and her daughter are trapped in an attic during a flood in Nashville, Tennessee.


Episode 2 - "Sharetha / Joe / John" - May 22, 2011

A pregnant woman living in Flint, Michigan is abducted, assaulted, and has her throat cut; a man survives a plane crash and is stranded in an icy river; and a man plays dead when his ex-co-worker shows up at the Warren, Ohio warehouse where he works and starts executing people.


Episode 3 - "Kara / Dan / Tamecka" - June 5, 2011

A teen girl is abducted and assaulted in Columbia, South Carolina; a photographer is trapped during the Haitian earthquake under debris in a hotel; and a Lancaster, Texas woman is beaten and slashed with scissors by her neighbor.


Episode 4 - "Jason / Dave and Joe / Martin" - June 12, 2011

Three Utah men go over waterfalls during a flash flood and fight to stay alive; a teenage boy from Portsmouth, Virginia is abducted and assaulted by a pedophile, then left to die chained in a box, buried under a thick layer of snow.


Episode 5 - "Julie / John" - June 19, 2011

A mother and her children are abducted from Palmetto Bay, Florida and taken to the Everglades; a man survives a bear attack in Lake Moses, Washington.


Episode 6 - "Harold / John / Lisa" - October 23, 2011

A store manager in Saint Louis is shot during a robbery, a Minot, North Dakota teen loses his arms in a farming accident, a girl from Tampa, Florida is kidnapped by a serial killer


Episode 7 - "Yvette / Jeremy and Jenny / Arkesha" - October 30, 2011

Outside Salt Lake City, Utah a 17 year old and her boyfriend are shot late one night, in the parking lot of the deserted reservoir they were hiking in. Two people's lives collide in a split second when two Los Angeles bound trains collide on the same track. A 14 year old, walking home from a school dance in New Orleans, Louisiana, is attacked 3 men- all at different times- in a hellish night she'll never forget.


Episode 8 - "Anita / Jim and Glen / Sabret" - November 6, 2011

A woman in Kokomo, Indiana is kidnapped, raped, and forced to live, chained up, in a metal box, for 13 days. 2 brothers are struck by lightning in a cabin at Yosemite National Park. A propane truck driver in Miami, Florida displays extraordinary courage when she is viciously beaten by a stranger.


Episode 9 - "Amy / Jeff / Tyler" - November 13, 2011

A De Soto, Missouri woman is raped and choked by a man she met at a party. A snowboarder is caught up in an avalanche. In Medicine Hat, Alberta, Canada, a 13-year-old boy and his 12-year-old friend spurned a school bully. They thought they were safe, until he shows up at one boy's home. After repeatedly sexually assaulting the 13-year-old, he slits both boy's throats, leaving them to die in a burning house.


Episode 10 - "Michelle / Terri-Lynn / Jennifer" - November 20, 2011

A Fort Wayne, Indiana woman is carjacked and raped. When a tornado sweeps through Huntsville, Alabama, a woman and her husband become trapped in their collapsed apartment complex, not knowing they're the only survivors in the entire building. An 8-year-old is abducted from her Dickinson, Texas condo and raped, before her attacker slits her throat and leaves her to die in a sawgrass prairie.


Episode 31 - "9/11 Survivors" - September 6, 2011

The stories of 12 survivors from the Sept. 11 attacks are recalled.
